entries.journal_entry_description: Send a message to Major Herand's Rebel contact that tells them the officer has been compromised and request aid in escaping Naboo. Travel to the rendezvous point, eliminate any Rebels present, and gather any data you can about other Rebel spies operating on Naboo.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Send a message to Major Hernad's Rebel contact that tells them the officer has been compromised and request aid in escaping Naboo. With luck, Major Herand's handlers will reveal themselves.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Travel to the rendezvous point and eliminate Major Herand's Rebel contacts. If you find any intel, take that as well.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Defeat Rebel troops at the rendezvous point.
entries.task04_item_name: You found a disk of Rebel intel
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Gather any intel you can from the area
